Ok%3D&h=e70cc63d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FFRAN6LHNSRBYJEUDAFJDMS65Y4%2F&h=206fd49a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/FRAN6LHNSRBYJEUDAFJDMS65Y4/</a>"}]}